# Install the Google Photo Viewer / Editor

### Install wine

~~~
sudo apt-get install wine
~~~

### Install winetricks

~~~
wget http://winetricks.org/winetricks
sudo mv winetricks /usr/local/bin
sudo chmod +x /usrc/local/bin/winetricks
~~~

### Install Picasa

~~~
wget http://dl.google.com/picasa/picasa39-setup.exe
wine ~/picasa39-setup.exe
~~~

### Run Picasa

Just type *picasa* in XMonad after Mod-P

### Configure Wine

Use program *winecfg*
